    public class AvroKeyCombineFileRecordReader
extends AvroKeyRecordReader<GenericRecord>
    A subclass of AvroKeyRecordReader. The purpose is to add a constructor with signature (CombineFileSplit, TaskAttemptContext, Integer), which is required in order to use CombineFileRecordReader.
